GNU DataExplorer - News - comes with version 3.1.9

1)  enable absolute time for graphics time line
2)  enable to set the font size of measurement values on digital display
3)  several processing optimizations
4)  fix caching algorithm to enable scale text color updated by color change 
5)  IISI-Cockpit V2 - add statistics definition 
6)  JetiAdapter - fix time step calculation for very short logs in respect of time
7)  JetiAdapter - fix record naming while repeating measurement names with different sensors
8)  HoTTAdapter* - update HoTTMdlViewer to latest 0.8 snapshot
9)  HoTTAdapter* - fine tune some more filter settings
10) HoTTAdapter* - add measurement voltage Rx min and make EAM rpm to an extra measurement
11) HoTTAdapter2 - fix missing update visibility status while switching record sets in display
12) UniLog2 - fix live data gathering capability
13) Futaba-Telemetry - fix english device properties file
14) OpenTx-Telemetry - add telemetry data support









